swine (0.7.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * QT4 migration         
  * Automatic winetricks menu creation
  * Major rewrite of all code
  * Moved images to resource file 
  * Internationalization support
  * German translation
  * Bugfix: using /UNIX when calling start with a unix path
  * Reimplemented LNK parser
  * Migrated from ini files to json
  * Using descriptions from LNK shortcuts
  * Added links to swine website and wine appdb
  * Added winetricks menu including winetricks download capability
  * Improved exception handler

